/*
 * $Id: ChangeLog,v 1.854 2003/03/18 22:12:25 ronpinkas Exp $
 */

/* Use this format for the entry headers:
   YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM UTC[-|+]hhmm Your Full Name <your_email@address>
   For example:
   2002-12-01 23:12 UTC+0100 Foo Bar <foo.bar@foobar.org>
*/

2003-03-19 00:48 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <ron@ronpinkas.com>
  * include/hbset.h
  * source/pp/pptable.c
  * source/rtl/set.c
  * source/rtl/traceprg.prg
    + Added support for:
       SET( _SET_TRACEFILE, <cFile> ) => cOldFile
       SET( _SET_TRACESTACK, <"NONE"|"CURRENT"|"ALL"> ) => cOldFile

  * source/rdd/nulsys/nulsys.prg
    + Added empty stubs needed to allow link of nulsys.lib in place of (rdd.lib + dbfntx.lib)

  * source/rtl/errorsys.prg
    * Modified log file logic to use macros to avoid forcing linkage of DB Functions (incase nulsys.lib is used).

