     space.
     Added the class function LOCATE. The bSoftSeek parameter must be used with
     a sorted field. I haven't fully test it. This function is not built for only
     sorted table. Perhaps an other function (like seek()) could be written for
     this (with a dicotomic search for example)? Any example of a search in a
     sorted table would be appreciated. Thanks
     bof() eof() gobottom() gotop() skip() working properly now

